Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:12.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}夕阳如火  我们就这样轻轻闭着双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:31.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}这悲伤太刻骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}被太阳公公晒湿了手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:39.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}这光彩太夺目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}日暮途穷回家路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:55.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}似是要沦陷 怪这晚霞艳艳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:59.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}明明再多一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:04.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我就至少能自爱一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:11.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}注意到这斜阳时早已闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:18.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}伴着傍晚的风平浪静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:26.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我们就这样轻轻闭着双眼
Comment: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.13,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ED「数センチメンタル」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:35.02,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(0,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}近づきそうな距離でも　わからなくなる夕暮れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:43.28,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}迷い込んでいる　迷路の　出口はどこか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.57,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}異常が日常になって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.57,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}反則だ　待て待て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.53,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}別に　どうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:52.24,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}素直になれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:56.12,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}いつまでも　このままでいたいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.13,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}そんな気持ちは溶けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:08.80,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕らは探してた　お揃いの心を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:16.93,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕らは交わしてた　まとまらないセリフを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:25.07,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}触れたい手の熱が　心まで届いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:33.16,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕は背伸びしてた　大人びてる君を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.79,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}知りたいんだ　君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.83,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}近づきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:40.96,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}夢じゃ足りなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.92,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}心が痛くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:47.26,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}もっと　言葉にしたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:35.02,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(0,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}夕阳下的我们是那么近  是那么懵懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:43.28,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}失去了方向  找寻不到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.57,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}不普通的日子成了日常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.57,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}这犯规了  你先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.53,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}其实都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:52.24,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我只是无法坦诚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:56.12,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}或许我想要永远这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.13,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}这份感情已溶于我心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:08.80,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我们一直在寻找  那颗成对的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:16.93,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我们一直在相互诉说  那不成文的一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:25.07,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}透过掌心的温暖  直击内心的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:33.16,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我一直在逞强  看着像个小大人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.79,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想要更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.83,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想靠近一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:40.96,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}不想只是梦到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.92,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}心里满是纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:47.26,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想告诉你
